# 🧾 Final Report – Simulated Tier 1 Help Desk Lab (Azure-Based)

## 📌 Overview

This project simulates a Tier 1 IT support environment using Microsoft Azure and Windows Server technologies. The lab includes user account management, Active Directory configuration, help desk ticket handling, and basic network troubleshooting.

---

## ☁️ Infrastructure Summary

- **Cloud Platform:** Microsoft Azure
- **VMs Used:**
  - Windows Server 2022 (Domain Controller)
  - Optional: Windows 10/11 client (Dev/Test)

- **Services Implemented:**
  - Active Directory Domain Services (AD DS)
  - DNS
  - Group Policy Management
  - Remote Desktop (RDP)

---

## 🛠️ Tasks Completed

- Created resource group, VNet, and VM in Azure
- Promoted server to domain controller (`helpdesk.local`)
- Created OUs, users, and security groups
- Simulated common help desk tickets
- Wrote documentation and how-to guides
- Tracked all issues with screenshots and resolution steps

